<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 00:36:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军将部队调往基地，那里有暴力暴徒抗议逮捕虐待加沙被拘留者的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-move-troops-to-base-where-mob-protested-arrest-of-soldiers-for-abusing-gaza-detainee/00000191-008a-d643-a1d1-b88eb6730001</link><description>周一，右翼抗议者袭击了两个军事基地，此前以色列国防军对“严重虐待一名巴勒斯坦被拘留者”进行了调查，九名预备役军人被捕。对北部战线进行数小时的局势评估</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 22:44:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-30/ty-article/.premium/idf-move-troops-to-base-where-mob-protested-arrest-of-soldiers-for-abusing-gaza-detainee/00000191-008a-d643-a1d1-b88eb6730001</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡否认哈马斯推迟协议的说法，称恐怖组织正在阻止协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-rejects-hamas-claims-of-delaying-deal-says-terror-group-is-preventing-it/00000190-ffc7-da63-a9d0-ffef50060000</link><description>以色列总理驳斥了哈马斯关于他通过增加新条件阻碍谈判的指控，并同样指责该恐怖组织修改了最初的纲要。与内塔尼亚胡的说法相反，消息人士证实以色列确实改进了其要求</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 19:25:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-rejects-hamas-claims-of-delaying-deal-says-terror-group-is-preventing-it/00000190-ffc7-da63-a9d0-ffef50060000</guid></item><item><title>在真主党的恐怖袭击之后，应该做出一个体面的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-29/ty-article/.highlight/out-of-the-hezbollah-horror-attack-one-decent-decision-should-emerge/00000190-ff4e-d88d-adb8-ff7e586b0000</link><description>以色列的民族国家法于 2018 年通过，正式将犹太人提升到高于其他公民的更高的特权地位。该法让德鲁兹人感到震惊，他们原本期望国家坚持其公民协议，并深感被背叛。法律应该废除</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 19:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-07-29/ty-article/.highlight/out-of-the-hezbollah-horror-attack-one-decent-decision-should-emerge/00000190-ff4e-d88d-adb8-ff7e586b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长在威胁“进入”以色列后将埃尔多安比作萨达姆·侯赛因</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-likens-erdogan-to-saddam-hussein-following-threat-to-enter-israel/00000190-ffa9-da63-a9d0-ffed3bd10000</link><description>在已经成为新常态的情况下，土耳其总统似乎威胁要因加沙战争而入侵以色列，引发以色列政界人士的强烈反对，称他为“想成为独裁者”，并警告说他的命运可能与已故伊拉克领导人萨达姆·侯赛因相似</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:55:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-fm-likens-erdogan-to-saddam-hussein-following-threat-to-enter-israel/00000190-ffa9-da63-a9d0-ffed3bd10000</guid></item><item><title>数十名抗议者袭击以色列军事基地，该基地关押着涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-far-right-protesters-break-into-idf-base-where-detained-soldiers-are-held/00000190-ffab-dfce-a990-fffb6d1d0000</link><description>士兵试图阻止数十名冲进基地并进入军事法庭大楼的抗议者，示威者称他们为“叛徒”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:43:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/dozens-of-far-right-protesters-break-into-idf-base-where-detained-soldiers-are-held/00000190-ffab-dfce-a990-fffb6d1d0000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列来说，贱民地位现在正在召唤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-march-of-folly-chapter-five-israel/00000190-feca-d22a-abfe-ffeae9500000</link><description>以色列的愚蠢行进始于 57 年前的六日战争之后，但在过去 18 个月里，极端主义的末日政府加剧了这一行径，该政府在深渊边缘时坚持要采取行动。向前迈出一步</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 18:11:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-march-of-folly-chapter-five-israel/00000190-feca-d22a-abfe-ffeae9500000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼议员攻击斯德·泰曼，试图给以色列军队带来混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/storming-of-sde-teiman-is-attempt-by-far-right-to-provoke-insurrection-in-the-idf/00000190-ff6e-da63-a9d0-ffefdf520000</link><description>自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列极右翼分子一直试图将其价值观强加于以色列国防军。周一，被指控虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的以色列预备役士兵在斯德泰曼拘留中心被拘留，这可能为他们提供了他们等待的机会</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 17:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/storming-of-sde-teiman-is-attempt-by-far-right-to-provoke-insurrection-in-the-idf/00000190-ff6e-da63-a9d0-ffefdf520000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡总理“强烈谴责”士兵被拘留后闯入斯德·泰曼监狱的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-strongly-condemns-break-in-into-sde-teiman-prison-over-soldiers-detention/00000190-fecd-d22a-abfe-ffed159c0000</link><description>涉嫌折磨一名巴勒斯坦被拘留者的九名士兵被拘留在斯德泰曼拘留中心，以及随后在该地点发生的冲突，导致以色列民选官员做出了强烈反应。艾萨克·赫尔佐格总统说：“我们不要忘记，我们的敌人一次又一次地试图追捕我们，在国际法律舞台上也是如此。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 16:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/pm-netanyahu-strongly-condemns-break-in-into-sde-teiman-prison-over-soldiers-detention/00000190-fecd-d22a-abfe-ffed159c0000</guid></item><item><title>杀害约旦河西岸以色列狱警的巴勒斯坦嫌疑人供认不讳</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspect-in-killing-of-israeli-prison-guard-in-west-bank-confesses/00000190-feb7-da9d-abff-ffff5a5e0000</link><description>军事法庭延长了对西岸银行嫌疑人易卜拉欣·曼苏尔的拘留令，据称他于 7 月初在吉文·哈达沙定居点杀害了尤海·阿夫尼，但杀人动机仍不清楚</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-suspect-in-killing-of-israeli-prison-guard-in-west-bank-confesses/00000190-feb7-da9d-abff-ffff5a5e0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔因不当行为调查而撤回以色列警察局长人选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-pick-for-israel-police-chief-withdraws-amid-investigations-of-misconduct/00000190-fecd-da63-a9d0-ffed93d20000</link><description>现任代理警察局长阿夫沙洛姆·佩莱德 (Avshalom Peled) 被曝因违反信任而受到多项调查，这导致他的任命被推迟。佩莱德退出后，本格维尔提出了新候选人</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 15:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-pick-for-israel-police-chief-withdraws-amid-investigations-of-misconduct/00000190-fecd-da63-a9d0-ffed93d20000</guid></item><item><title>对 Majdal Shams 悲剧的反应表明阿拉伯人对以色列的德鲁兹人感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/reactions-to-majdal-shams-tragedy-show-arab-confusion-about-the-druze-in-israel/00000190-fdc8-d807-a1b2-ffebb6ea0000</link><description>社交媒体上的一些人庆祝戈兰高地发生的致命袭击，这场袭击造成 12 名儿童死亡，以此作为对以色列轰炸加沙的报复。其他人质疑在了解以色列的德鲁兹人复杂的历史之前是否应该同情他们</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 14:35:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/reactions-to-majdal-shams-tragedy-show-arab-confusion-about-the-druze-in-israel/00000190-fdc8-d807-a1b2-ffebb6ea0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么巴黎奥运会开幕式激怒了欧洲极右翼分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-enrages-europes-far-right/00000190-fe0f-d88d-adb8-ff3f1b910000</link><description>这个历史悠久的歌舞表演中的每一个图像都旨在描绘一个新的、多元文化的法国，对任何性别或性取向开放。组织者设法既杀死了神圣的牛又不留下干眼症</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 13:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-enrages-europes-far-right/00000190-fe0f-d88d-adb8-ff3f1b910000</guid></item><item><title>凯撒利亚之战：占领以色列最富裕社区之一的令人惊讶的冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-of-caesarea-will-the-fall-of-netanyahus-rule-start-at-home/00000190-f9cd-da13-a5d5-fdff64930000</link><description>在总理居住的凯撒利亚，反内塔尼亚胡的抗议活动日益增多，在这座富裕的小镇引起了轩然大波。 “凯撒利亚反映了整个国家面临的问题——大量的仇恨和分裂，以及沉默的大多数”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-battle-of-caesarea-will-the-fall-of-netanyahus-rule-start-at-home/00000190-f9cd-da13-a5d5-fdff64930000</guid></item><item><title>军警拘留涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-police-raid-sde-teiman-prison-detain-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-detainee/00000190-fe2c-d22a-abfe-ff2c10c20000</link><description>据报道，以色列预备役士兵与警察对峙并封锁自己，向前来拘留嫌疑人的军事人员喷洒胡椒喷雾，抗议者闯入拘留中心 ■ 这些士兵因有报道称他们虐待一名巴勒斯坦囚犯而被拘留</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-police-raid-sde-teiman-prison-detain-soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-detainee/00000190-fe2c-d22a-abfe-ff2c10c20000</guid></item><item><title>在迈季代勒沙姆斯炸死 12 名儿童的火箭弹也触动了戈兰德鲁兹派与以色列关系的痛处</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-rocket-that-killed-12-children-hit-a-nerve-in-israels-relations-with-the-golan-druze/00000190-fe00-d22a-abfe-ff282afc0000</link><description>在经历了该社区历史上最悲惨的一天之后，戈兰高地德鲁兹人的独特处境凸显出来。夹在长期的叙利亚身份和与以色列日益加深的联系之间，特别是在年轻人中，这个人口少而紧密的人口面临着不确定的未来</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 11:35:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/the-rocket-that-killed-12-children-hit-a-nerve-in-israels-relations-with-the-golan-druze/00000190-fe00-d22a-abfe-ff282afc0000</guid></item><item><title>美国警告黎巴嫩公民：“在危机开始之前离开”；航空公司取消飞往贝鲁特、特拉维夫的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/major-airlines-cancel-delay-flights-to-beirut-as-fear-of-major-israel-hezbollah-war-looms/00000190-fdb0-da13-a5d5-fdfb8c570000</link><description>汉莎航空、法航、土耳其航空、爱琴航空等主要航空公司决定推迟和取消飞往黎巴嫩唯一国际机场贝鲁特拉菲克·哈里里机场的航班</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:24:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/major-airlines-cancel-delay-flights-to-beirut-as-fear-of-major-israel-hezbollah-war-looms/00000190-fdb0-da13-a5d5-fdfb8c570000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队指挥官下令炸毁拉法水库。以色列国防军怀疑违反国际法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-commanders-gave-order-to-blow-up-rafah-reservoir-army-suspects-breach-of-intl-law/00000190-fd90-d5ef-a5fe-ff9ec3ea0000</link><description>装甲兵炸毁水库的行为得到了指挥官的批准，但没有得到高级军官的同意。一名士兵在社交媒体上发布了视频，称其为“纪念安息日”。军方将决定是否展开正式调查</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 09:09:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-commanders-gave-order-to-blow-up-rafah-reservoir-army-suspects-breach-of-intl-law/00000190-fd90-d5ef-a5fe-ff9ec3ea0000</guid></item><item><title>Majdal Shams 的杀戮场上：巨大而平静的悲伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-killing-field-in-majdal-shams-a-great-but-quiet-grief/00000190-fd05-d7a2-a9b0-ff656e950000</link><description>德鲁兹小镇迈季达勒沙姆斯是一个风景如画、安静的山脚下的地方，在来自黎巴嫩的火箭弹袭击造成 12 名儿童和青少年死亡后，这座小镇陷入了彻底的震动。一位居民说：“他们是我们大家的孩子。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 08:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article-magazine/.premium/on-the-killing-field-in-majdal-shams-a-great-but-quiet-grief/00000190-fd05-d7a2-a9b0-ff656e950000</guid></item><item><title>我出生在以色列。我哪儿也不去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/i-was-born-in-israel-i-am-not-going-anywhere/00000190-fd2e-da13-a5d5-fd7ff3750000</link><description>因为我也是土著，所以我不打算搬家。哈马斯不会让我搬家，贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇或伊塔马尔·本-格维尔也不会</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 07:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/.premium/i-was-born-in-israel-i-am-not-going-anywhere/00000190-fd2e-da13-a5d5-fd7ff3750000</guid></item><item><title>11 岁德鲁兹男孩被确认为真主党火箭袭击的第 12 名受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/11-year-old-druze-boy-identified-as-12th-victim-of-hezbollah-rocket-attack/00000190-fb20-d43d-afd2-ff3a23a00000</link><description>对火箭袭击现场发现的证据进行的 DNA 测试证实了格瓦拉·易卜拉欣 (Gevara Ebraheem) 的死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 06:26:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-07-29/ty-article/11-year-old-druze-boy-identified-as-12th-victim-of-hezbollah-rocket-attack/00000190-fb20-d43d-afd2-ff3a23a00000</guid></item></channel></rss>